  "Description": {
    "English": "Succulent, edible cactus flesh from the <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Echinocactus plant</span>. As well as being juicy on the tongue, the flesh has many industrial uses.<br><br>The Echinocactus thrives only on <span class=\"name name-fuel\">desert planets</span>, but can be farmed in all environments with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hydroponics Tray</span>..",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "来自<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">金琥植物</span>的多汁、可食用的仙人掌肉。仙人掌肉不仅多汁鲜美，还具有许多工业用途。<br><br>金琥只能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">沙漠星球</span>上生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TencentChinese": "来自<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">金琥植物</span>的多汁、可食用的仙人掌肉。仙人掌肉不仅多汁鲜美，还具有许多工业用途。<br><br>金琥只能在<span class=\"name name-fuel\">沙漠星球</span>上生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "多汁、可食用的多肉植物果肉，取自<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">仙人球植物</span>。除了汁多味美之外，果肉也有多種工業用途。<br><br>仙人球僅能生長於<span class=\"name name-fuel\">沙漠環境</span>，但若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">水耕盤</span>，便能在任何環境中栽種。"
  },
